er 2014 || Entire Game on One Screen || || 2637 || Daniel Linssen || ''birdsong'' || Simon Larsen<br />Lukas Hansen<br />Frederik Storm || ''90 Second Portraits'' || <ref>{{cite web|title=Ludum Dare 31 Results|url=http://ludumdare.com/compo/ludum-dare-31/?more=1|work=Ludum Dare|accessdate=December 30, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n| 32 || April 2015 || An Unconventional Weapon || || 2821 || 01010111 || ''\uff22\uff25\uff24\u2730\uff28\uff2f\uff27\uff27''  || Bogdan Rybak<br />Igor Puzhevich<br />Zi Ye<br />Megan Alcock || ''The Rock the Paper and the Scissors'' || <ref>{{cite web|title=Ludum Dare 32 Results|url=http://ludumdare.com/compo/ludum-dare-32/|work=Ludum Dare|accessdate=May 11, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 33 || August 2015 || You are the Monster || || 2725 || DragonXVI || ''Writhe: The Thing from the Omega Sector'' || Pietro Ferrantelli<br/>Theophile Loaec<br/>Augustin Grassien<br/>OrikMcFly || ''Mobs, Inc.'' || <ref>{{cite web|title=Ludum Dare 33 Results|url=http://ludumdare.com/compo/ludum-dare-33/|work=Ludum Dare|accessdate=September 16, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n| 34 || December 2015 || Growing/two button controls || || 2870 || vegapomme27 || ''Frank & Stein'' || Big Green Pillow ft Mgaia || ''Slash Quest'' || <ref>{{cite web|title=Ludum Dare 34 Results|url=http://ludumdare.com/compo/ludum-dare-34/|work=Ludum Dare|accessdate=January 4, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| 35 || April 2016 || Shapeshift ||  || 2718 ||  Daniel Linssen\n||''windowframe''||  Barney Cumming<br />Dave Lloyd<br />Jon Murphy<br />Paul Dal Pozzo<br />Louis Meyer<br />Adrian Vaughan\n||  ''The Maitre D''\n|| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://ludumdare.com/compo/ludum-dare-35/|title=Ludum Dare 35 Results|work=Ludum Dare|accessdate=December 2, 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| 36 || August 2016\u2021 || Ancient Technology ||  ||  1912\n||  No ratings\n||N/A||No ratings\n||N/A\n||  <ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ludumdare.com/compo/2016/08/24/welcome-to-ludum-dare-36/|title=Welcome to Ludum Dare 36! {{!}} Ludum Dare|website=ludumdare.com|language=en-U