 Team'' || Graeme Borland || ''NXTWPN10'' || <ref>{{cite web|last=Polson|first=John|title=2,213 free games ranked for your pleasure: Ludum Dare 27 results|url=http://indiegames.com/2013/09/2213_free_game_picks_ranked_fo.html|work=Indie Games|publisher=UBM Tech|accessdate=January 9, 2014|date=September 18, 2013}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=NXTWPN10|url=http://www.graemeborland.com/games/nxtwpn10/|work=Graeme Borland|accessdate=January 9, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n| 28 || December 2013 || You only get one || || 2064 || Dani\u00ebl Haazen || ''One Take'' || Mark Foster<br />David Fenn<br />Andrew Gleeson || ''[[Titan Souls]]'' || <ref>{{cite web|last=LeRay|first=Lena|title=Free Games: Ludum Dare 28 results posted|url=http://indiegames.com/2014/01/free_games_ludum_dare_28_resul.html|work=Indie Games|publisher=UBM Tech|accessdate=January 9, 2014|date=January 8, 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Ludum Dare 28|url=http://www.ludumdare.com/compo/ludum-dare-28/?action=preview|work=Ludum Dare|accessdate=January 9, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n| 29 || April 2014 || Beneath the surface || || 2497 ||  Daniel Linssen\n|| ''The Sun and Moon'' || Shannon Mason<br />Richard Lems<br />Diane de Wilde || ''ScubaBear'' || <ref>{{cite web|title=Ludum Dare 29 Results|url=http://www.ludumdare.com/compo/ludum-dare-29/|work=Ludum Dare|accessdate=May 19, 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Polson|first=John|title=2,500 games lead to two platformer winners for Ludum Dare 29|url=http://indiegames.com/2014/05/2500_games_and_two_winners_fro.html|work=Indie Games|publisher=UBM Tech|accessdate=May 23, 2014|date=May 19, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n| 30 || August 2014 || Connected Worlds || || 2538 || PixelMind || ''SuperDimensional'' || Kevin Zuhn<br />Kevin Geisler<br />Chris Stallman<br />Devon Scott-Tunkin || ''Antbassador'' || <ref>{{cite web|title=Ludum Dare 30 Results|url=http://www.ludumdare.com/compo/ludum-dare-30/?action=top|work=Ludum Dare|accessdate=September 16, 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Ludum Dare 30 Results|u